<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Forfeo Lab | Excellence Client 2025</title>
    <style>
        :root { --primary: #00aaff; --dark: #0a0a0a; --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--dark); color: white; overflow-x: hidden; }

        /* Loader Futuriste */
        #loader { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: var(--dark); z-index: 9999; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: opacity 0.5s; }
        .scanner { width: 250px; height: 3px; background: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 25px var(--primary); animation: scan 2.5s infinite ease-in-out; }
        @keyframes scan { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(-60px); opacity: 0.2; } 50% { transform: translateY(60px); opacity: 1; } }

        nav { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; padding: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 40px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); z-index: 1000; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
        nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: 0.3s; opacity: 0.7; }
        nav a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--primary); }

        .hero { height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 0 20px; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 5rem; margin: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff 30%, var(--primary) 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        
        .auth-grid { display: flex; gap: 30px; margin-top: 50px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
        .glass-card { background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 25px; padding: 40px; width: 380px; transition: 0.4s; }
        .glass-card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-5px); }

        input { width: 100%; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); border: 1px solid #333; color: white; border-radius: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; }
        input:focus { border-color: var(--primary); }
        .btn { width: 100%; padding: 15px; border: none; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 170, 255, 0.4); }
        .btn-outline { background: transparent; border: 1px solid white; color: white; }

        .mission-section { padding: 100px 20px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
        .mission-box { background: var(--glass); padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--primary); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="loader">
        <div class="scanner"></div>
        <p style="margin-top: 40px; letter-spacing: 5px; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.6;">AUTHENTIFICATION SYSTÈME...</p>
    </div>

    <nav>
        <a href="/">ACCUEIL</a>
        <a href="/business-plans">SOLUTIONS</a>
        <a href="/partenaires">ÉCOSYSTÈME</a>
        <a href="/candidature">AMBASSADEURS</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Forfeo Lab</h1>
        <p style="max-width: 700px; font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.7; line-height: 1.6;">
            Le premier laboratoire d'audit hybride combinant l'intelligence artificielle Forfy et l'expertise d'ambassadeurs certifiés pour une expérience client sans faille.
        </p>

        <div class="auth-grid">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Connexion Business</h3>
                <form action="/login-entreprise" method="POST">
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email professionnel" required>
                    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Mot de passe" required>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">DÉVERROUILLER LE DASHBOARD</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-section">
        <div class="mission-box">
            <h3>01. Audit</h3>
            <p style="opacity: 0.6;">Nos ambassadeurs s'immergent incognito dans votre écosystème pour capturer la réalité du terrain.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-box">
            <h3>02. Analyse</h3>
            <p style="opacity: 0.6;">L'IA Forfy traite les données brutes pour extraire les points de friction critiques.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-box">
            <h3>03. Action</h3>
            <p style="opacity: 0.6;">Recevez des recommandations stratégiques immédiates pour augmenter votre rétention client.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section id="signup" style="padding: 100px 0; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Prêt à optimiser vos standards ?</h2>
        <div class="glass-card" style="margin: 40px auto; width: 450px;">
            <form action="/signup-entreprise" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="nom" placeholder="Nom de votre compagnie" required>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email de contact" required>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Créer un mot de passe" required>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline">LANCER MON LABORATOIRE</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/forfy') %>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
            const loader = document.getElementById('loader');
            loader.style.opacity = '0';
            setTimeout(() => loader.style.display = 'none', 500);
        });

        document.querySelectorAll('a, form button').forEach(el => {
            el.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                if(el.tagName === 'A' && el.getAttribute('href').startsWith('#')) return;
                const loader = document.getElementById('loader');
                loader.style.display = 'flex';
                loader.style.opacity = '1';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
